# Version AGENTS.md after edits

Whenever you modify **AGENTS.md**, run this right after saving:

```bash
bash scripts/commit-agents-md.sh
```

Run it from the project root. The script only creates a commit if AGENTS.md actually changed. This keeps a local version history so the agent (or user) can revert if needed.
